      "score": 13,
      "comments": 25,
      "author": "caius",
      "published": "2026-06-15T09:46:08Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Prioritize building side projects, creating POCs, and experimenting with modern languages like Rust, Go, or Zig.",
        "Optimize engineering velocity by refactoring legacy code, automating CI/CD pipelines, and resolving accumulated technical debt.",
        "Invest in continuous learning, studying distributed systems architecture, and evaluating database performance metrics."
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "hackernews",
