      "score": 196,
      "comments": 144,
      "author": "chmaynard",
      "published": "2026-06-15T20:12:37Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Interviewers heavily test Kubernetes control plane internals, etcd consistency, and CNI networking over basic YAML writing or application deployment.",
        "Practical GitOps experience with ArgoCD or Flux and Day-2 observability using Prometheus are highly valued over theoretical cluster administration.",
        "Candidates must demonstrate hands-on troubleshooting of DNS resolution, OOMKilled errors, and cost-efficient scaling using Karpenter or Cluster Autoscaler."
      ]
    },
